CustomField.description: Indicates whether the timecard is excluded from the maximum number of hours set in the max-resource-hours-per-day configuration option that can be entered per day for a resource. See "max-resource-hours-per-day".
CustomField.inlineHelpText: Indicates whether the timecard is excluded from the maximum number of hours set in the max-resource-hours-per-day configuration option that can be entered per day for a resource. See "max-resource-hours-per-day".
CustomField.label: Exclude from Daily Maximum
